XM23 n23 WL2 SL2 GND sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 L=0.5 W=1.5 nf=1 ad=0.435 as=0.435
+ pd=3.58 ps=3.58 nrd=0.193 nrs=0.193 sa=0 sb=0 sd=0 mult=1
